# Pre-Release Readiness

Release work must satisfy **`.ai/RELEASING.md`** gates before publish (maintainer long-form: `docs/maintainers/RELEASING.md` when editing policy):

- scope and changelog complete
- validation checks pass
- migration/security impacts reviewed
- required evidence captured

If any gate is open, do not publish.

